<bibRefCitation id="EFAA4B57FFC1C21DF23A3D4CFDE69D8D" author="Przybylowicz" box="[319,532,1400,1423]" pageId="5" pageNumber="59" refString="Przybylowicz, L. (2009) Thyretini of Africa. An Illustrated Catalogue of the Thyretini (Lepidoptera: Arctiidae: Syntominae) of the Afrotropical Region. Entomonograph Series, Vol. 16, Apollo Books, Stenstrup, 170 pp." type="book" year="2009">
